room_title: Escape room "Starship Genesis" by Race to Escape in Tampa
review: This was a great experience! The place was so clean and neat. The decor was on point and so very well-thought-out. The staff was fun to be around and accommodating. The price is right for such a wonderful experience with friends. Thank you!

room_title: Escape room "Starship Genesis" by Race to Escape in Tampa
review: Best time ever!!! Outstanding job on the decorations the rooms the way everything was set up!! Definitely will do it again!! It's was a girls night out and this was the best thing!! Can't wait to try another room and do it again well laid out and set up on everything!!!
